cli/output/color_test.go contains a battery of representative Result values; for each, asserts stripANSI(ColorPresenter.X(r)) == PlainPresenter.X(r) for every Presenter method X. The test is parameterized across all 12 built-in themes: every theme's output, when ANSI-stripped, must equal Plain. Battery covers: synced, drifted marker, drifted spec, deleted spec, deleted marker, no-baseline, multi-edge expanded, --all with multiple edges, empty state, unlinked warning, OkResult, ErrorResult (with and without hint), TextResult, VersionResult.